{"tid":2249385,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新城市廣場扶手電梯寫「香港獨立」 17歲女生認刑毀 續准保釋候判","createTime":"2020-10-19T09:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:37:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"357d0ad9a2fae0489774c06ad81095d1b7211a7a","tid":2249385,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"反修例運動6.12一周年當天，各區均有示威活動。兩名中五女生被指在沙田新城市廣場扶手電梯塗鴉，寫上「香港獨立」字句，被控刑事損壞罪。其中一位女生早前認罪，另一名女生今亦認罪。其代表律師求情指，被告已明白錯誤，往後會以合法方式關心社會，對造成新城市廣場不便致歉。署理主任裁判官溫紹明下令被告向商場賠償4,500元清潔費，案件押後至下月19日判刑，其間被告獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/UX6QMXP3MBCV5I67I3MSSTD2QA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FUX6QMXP3MBCV5I67I3MSSTD2QA%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=ca3eebdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FUX6QMXP3MBCV5I67I3MSSTD2QA%2F&h=96eb2749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/UX6QMXP3MBCV5I67I3MSSTD2QA/</a>"},{"pid":"f8709a52ce260578209ff369b963f5bac629228a","tid":2249385,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242b273933777b11c1414dee90a4c28226f05216","tid":2249385,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"357d0ad9a2fae0489774c06ad81095d1b7211a7a","tid":2249385,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"反修例運動6.12一周年當天，各區均有示威活動。兩名中五女生被指在沙田新城市廣場扶手電梯塗鴉，寫上「香港獨立」字句，被控刑事損壞罪。其中一位女生早前認罪，另一名女生今亦認罪。其代表律師求情指，被告已明白錯誤，往後會以合法方式關心社會，對造成新城市廣場不便致歉。署理主任裁判官溫紹明下令被告向商場賠償4,500元清潔費，案件押後至下月19日判刑，其間被告獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/202010